INSTALLAZIONE
1- Creare LXC Ubuntu LTS
2- Aggiungere mountpoint per disco
      # nano /etc/pve/lxc/XXX.conf
      # mp0: /mnt/hdd-data,mp=/mnt/hdd-data,ro=0
3- Installare CockPit - https://cockpit-project.org/running#ubuntu
4- Installare 45Drives - https://github.com/45Drives/cockpit-file-sharing
5- Installare WSDD - https://github.com/christgau/wsdd

